OL,7,FIt is understood that a commitment of
OL,8,F#45million is being sought, which,
OL,9,Faccording to a feasibility study
OL,10,Fconducted by Athletic Ventures, would
OL,11,Fgenerate an economic and social impact
OL,12,Fof more than #400m.
OL,14,FThe letter reads: "We write as
OL,15,Fathletes who have had the honour of
OL,16,Frepresenting Great Britain and
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland on the world stage.
OL,18,FAmong us are World, Olympic, European
OL,19,Fand Commonwealth champions and
OL,20,Fmedallists.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
