OL,3,CAthletics stars want Government to
OL,4,Cback London bid for 2029 world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,F"We've stood on podiums with pride but
OL,8,Fthere is nothing like competing in
OL,9,Ffront of a home crowd. For many
OL,10,Fathletes, it's a once-in-a-lifetime
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,F"For our country, it's an opportunity
OL,14,Fwe must not let pass us by.
OL,16,F"That's why we are calling on the UK
OL,17,FGovernment to back the bid to host the
OL,18,FWorld Athletics Championships in 2029.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
