OL,3,CAthletics stars want Government to
OL,4,Cback London bid for 2029 world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,F"There is no more iconic setting than
OL,8,Fthe London Stadium, the scene of
OL,9,Funforgettable moments at the 2012
OL,10,FOlympic and Paralympic Games, and the
OL,11,Frecord-breaking 2017 World
OL,12,FChampionships.
OL,14,F"Britain knows how to put on global
OL,15,Fevents. We do it brilliantly. And when
OL,16,Fwe host, the impact goes far beyond
OL,17,Fmedals and headlines. It inspires a
OL,18,Fgeneration. It generates huge economic
OL,19,Fand community impact. It brings the
OL,20,Fcountry together in excitement and
OL,21,Fjoy."
