OL,7,FOther signatories include two-time
OL,8,Fworld heptathlon champion and Paris
OL,9,F2024 Olympic silver medallist Katarina
OL,10,FJohnson-Thompson, double Athens 2004
OL,11,FOlympic gold medallist Dame Kelly
OL,12,FHolmes, 2023 world 1500 metres
OL,13,Fchampion Josh Kerr and 2019 world 200
OL,14,Fmetres champion Dina Asher-Smith.
OL,16,FA steer in the spending review would
OL,17,Fgive an indication that the bid has
OL,18,Fnot been forgotten.
