OL,4,Cback London bid for 2029 world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FThe funding itself would not be
OL,8,Frequired until 2028, but the finance
OL,9,Fneeds to be guaranteed by September,
OL,10,Fthe deadline for organisers to submit
OL,11,Fa formal expression of interest to
OL,12,FWorld Athletics.
OL,14,FA successful bid would see London host
OL,15,Fthe world championships for the first
OL,16,Ftime since 2017, an event that boasted
OL,17,Fa sold-out stadium for every session.
OL,19,FThe Department for Digital, Culture,
OL,20,FMedia and Sport (DCMS) has been
OL,21,Fcontacted by PA for comment.
