OL,7,FThe letter continues: "We know there
OL,8,Fare tough decisions facing the
OL,9,Fcountry. But this isn't just about
OL,10,Fsport. It's about opportunity,
OL,11,Finclusion, wellbeing`and pride.
OL,13,F"Events like this bring economic
OL,14,Fbenefit, drive tourism, and showcase
OL,15,FBritain at its best. But above all,
OL,16,Fthey leave a legacy that lives on in
OL,17,Fcommunities, schools and families for
OL,18,Fyears to come.
